OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud and rain initially over
OL,6,FShetland. Mix of brighter spells and
OL,7,Flight showers reaching all late
OL,8,Fmorning. Showers building during
OL,9,Fafternoon, perhaps merging to longer
OL,10,Fperiods rain late afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will be mostly cloudy
OL,13,Fthrough the evening and overnight with
OL,14,Fshowers or longer spells of rain,
OL,15,Fheavy at times. Occasionally breezy
OL,16,Ffor Orkney.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
