OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA cloudy start with showers
OL,6,For longer spells of rain, turning
OL,7,Fdrier with bright spells developing
OL,8,Flater. Breezy at first for Orkney,
OL,9,Feasing later.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,12,Fand Monday will be dry with sunny
OL,13,Fspells and variable cloud. Dry start
OL,14,Fon Tuesday with bright or sunny
OL,15,Fspells, rain and freshening winds
OL,16,Fspreading northeast later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
